snippet.textDisplay:
Absolutely fantastic!! Thanks a lot guys for giving us master piece like this. And the video, how everyone is committed in the moment created completely amazing atmosphere. I lost it couple of times but can’t help stop watching. Love everyone’s contribution.
I am living in Germany for last four years but very old fan of Arnob and Mizan. I cannot describe how great it feels when I hear my Non-Bengali friends also love them and also sings those melodies. <3 <3
snippet.textOriginal:
Absolutely fantastic!! Thanks a lot guys for giving us master piece like this. And the video, how everyone is committed in the moment created completely amazing atmosphere. I lost it couple of times but can’t help stop watching. Love everyone’s contribution.
I am living in Germany for last four years but very old fan of Arnob and Mizan. I cannot describe how great it feels when I hear my Non-Bengali friends also love them and also sings those melodies. <3 <3
